# Flash freely

It is always OK to build and flash the MT4 jog firmware (`python flash_jog.py`) without asking for confirmation.

- Do it whenever firmware changes land, or when the user says "flash".
- Free COM9 first if needed (stop `jog.py`, `map_envelope.py`, `mt4_mcp`, etc.) — only one process may own the serial port.
- Prefer flashing over leaving unflashed firmware changes on disk.
